{"tid":522162,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"贏了跟我在一起！南韓格鬥家告白舉牌正妹 結果被打爆","createTime":"2018-01-07T09:35:15.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-07T10:21:24.000Z","uid":34498,"like":10,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"cf7a65834e42926df94925a92a118c2bcebec6da","tid":522162,"uid":34498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-07T09:35:15.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">贏了跟我在一起！南韓格鬥家告白舉牌正妹 結果被打爆</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/liveNews/BigPic/600_phpClyYpt.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2FliveNews%2FBigPic%2F600_phpClyYpt.jpg&h=8adccbea&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n舉牌女郎李恩惠身材火辣，在IG上有12.2萬人追蹤。（翻攝自IG:eunhyeato）<br />\n<br />\n〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕「路德國際綜合格鬥大賽45期」（RFC45）在南韓首爾開打，28歲的南韓地主選手信康昊頗被看好，他甚至在賽前向舉牌女郎李恩惠告白，李恩惠也公開回應「如果信康昊打贏了，我就和他在一起！」沒想到信康昊被美國選手巴瑞特（Chris barrnet）一陣痛打，第二回合就遭到TKO（技術擊倒），只能心酸地看著心上人頒獎給對手。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/liveNews/BigPic/600_php70pm0d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2FliveNews%2FBigPic%2F600_php70pm0d.jpg&h=719ce49e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n信康昊（右2）在賽前公開向李恩惠（右1）獻花告白，表示「如果我贏了這場比賽，請跟我交往！」。（翻攝自網路）<br />\n<br />\n綜合媒體報導，188公分、135公斤的信康昊是南韓格鬥界的新星，也被視為本屆賽事的熱門選手。他賽前向有12萬人追蹤的舉牌女郎李恩惠獻花告白，表示「如果我贏了這場比賽，請跟我交往！」李恩惠也在IG上甜蜜相許，讓這場比賽瀰漫著粉紅泡泡。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/liveNews/BigPic/600_phpYb5AD8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2FliveNews%2FBigPic%2F600_phpYb5AD8.jpg&h=0871d440&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n正式開打時，信康昊遭到對手巴瑞特完全壓制，頭部、腹部等要害頻頻遭到痛打。（翻攝自網路）<br />\n<br />\n沒想到，正式開打時，信康昊遭到對手巴瑞特完全壓制，頭部、腹部等要害頻頻遭到痛打，到了第二回合中後段就因為體力不支，被裁判宣布TKO，只能落寞地看著李恩惠頒獎給對手。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/liveNews/BigPic/600_phpzVtiNh.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2FliveNews%2FBigPic%2F600_phpzVtiNh.jpg&h=9aae0253&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n眼看信康昊居於劣勢，李恩惠神情略顯憂心。（翻攝自網路）<br />\n<br />\n信康昊的戰敗引起南韓酸民狂批，嘲諷他賽前整天想著女人，看起來一點都沒準備，被慘虐也是活該。而信康昊與李恩惠原本甜蜜的約定，如今也讓雙方尷尬無比，暫時沒有後續消息。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/liveNews/BigPic/600_phpJfdgmg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2FliveNews%2FBigPic%2F600_phpJfdgmg.jpg&h=5b9d81ca&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n到了第二回合中後段，信康昊因為體力不支，被裁判宣布TKO。（翻攝自網路）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/liveNews/BigPic/600_phps2mQ8U.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2FliveNews%2FBigPic%2F600_phps2mQ8U.jpg&h=05819bbd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n最後信康昊只能落寞地看著李恩惠頒獎給對手。（翻攝自網路）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2304477?utm_medium=P\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2304477%3Futm_medium%3DP&d=4Hjs%2BmuqsxpMn9N80J9o0jA5unq%2FSd9ZKvr75NUD1%2F0%3D&h=bdddd65c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2304477%3Futm_medium%3DP&h=7044c82a\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2304477?utm_medium=P</a>"},{"pid":"1d243b05c9075986b91ca41b9d3c150cd8797ff6","tid":522162,"uid":34498,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-07T09:37:37.000Z","msg":"泡狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"97537d6a8c7682a7c506648f03196de3cc7ec8de","tid":522162,"uid":97814,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-07T09:38:00.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"39873602b487af13bbee52b8413a84b7d03eb42f","tid":522162,"uid":34498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"97537d6a8c7682a7c506648f03196de3cc7ec8de","tid":522162,"uid":97814,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-07T09:38:00.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"rep